If you don't get up right now,

12
00:00:46,312 --> 00:00:47,380
I'm gonna kiss you.

13
00:01:18,812 --> 00:01:20,112
Finally, Tianyou isn't around today.

14
00:01:20,113 --> 00:01:21,081
Can you stop texting

15
00:01:21,081 --> 00:01:22,048
