24
00:01:32,826 --> 00:01:33,866
Then give me a kiss first.

25
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:34,960
No.

26
00:01:37,430 --> 00:01:37,964
You have no idea

27
00:01:37,965 --> 00:01:39,699
