30
00:01:44,404 --> 00:01:45,805
We're just friends.

31
00:01:46,172 --> 00:01:47,307
Don't listen to the gossip.

32
00:01:48,908 --> 00:01:49,709
Zhou You...

33
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:50,943
