34
00:01:50,944 --> 00:01:52,412
Zhou Youzhi, think carefully.

35
00:01:52,779 --> 00:01:54,013
It's either him or me.

36
00:01:56,149 --> 00:01:57,149
Take your pick.

37
00:01:57,717 --> 00:01:58,885
Stop being so dramatic, okay?

38
00:02:00,253 --> 00:02:01,253
Fine.

39
00:02:05,225 --> 00:02:06,559
That's weird.

40
00:02:06,860 --> 00:02:08,728
He always picks up my calls.

41
00:02:09,229 --> 00:02:10,496
Smart of him.

42
00:02:10,497 --> 00:02:11,364
I told him

43
00:02:11,365 --> 00:02:12,498
