44
00:02:12,499 --> 00:02:13,733
You're spending today with me.

45
00:02:32,685 --> 00:02:34,220
Maybe it's better if I just leave.

46
00:02:51,170 --> 00:02:52,170
Professor,

47
00:02:52,338 --> 00:02:53,805
